m\": \"his body\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3925}, {\"ngram\": \"the first few steps\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 3983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After those, he gauges where he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s sprinting in his lane\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094in the middle, always, is the ideal.\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 4081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4020}, {\"ngram\": \"his lane\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094in\", \"from\": 4034, \"to\": 4047}, {\"ngram\": \"the ideal\", \"from\": 4071, \"to\": 4080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Past 10 meters, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s driving, legs churning, slowly \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cputting more force into the ground.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Around 20 meters, his body, hips and chest slowly begin to rise.\", \"from\": 4083, \"to\": 4244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4105}, {\"ngram\": \"more force\", \"from\": 4148, \"to\": 4158}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Around 20 meters\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4195}, {\"ngram\": \"his body\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4205}, {\"ngram\": \"hips\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4211}, {\"ngram\": \"chest\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No jerking, hence the ramp up.\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No jerking\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4255}, {\"ngram\": \"hence the ramp\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 4271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After 30 meters, his hips come underneath him, his chest rises and his shoulders remain forward, as he drives down the track.\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"30 meters\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4292}, {\"ngram\": \"his hips\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4302}, {\"ngram\": \"his shoulders\", \"from\": 4344, \"to\": 4357}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 4392, \"to\": 4401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At that point, he wants to be standing up, raising his knees high and stamping them right back down on the track like pistons.\", \"from\": 4403, \"to\": 4529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4416}, {\"ngram\": \"his knees\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4463}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4515}, {\"ngram\": \"pistons\", \"from\": 4521, \"to\": 4528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cPushing your momentum down the track, almost as if, like, you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re falling,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says in the video.\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your momentum\", \"from\": 4541, \"to\": 4554}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 4560, \"to\": 4569}, {\"ngram\": \"you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4599}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He gauges, again, his placement within his lane.\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his placement\", \"from\": 4653, \"to\": 4666}, {\"ngram\": \"his lane\", \"from\": 4674, \"to\": 4682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s too inside, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ccutting that stride\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d too much, losing energy and speed.\", \"from\": 4684, \"to\": 4773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4687, \"to\": 4693}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4762}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 4767, \"to\": 4772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s outside in his lane, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s running \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ctoo much track.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Think: golfer who bombs drives but elongates holes by spraying them far right or far left.\", \"from\": 4774, \"to\": 4932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his lane\", \"from\": 4795, \"to\": 4803}, {\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4811}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ctoo much track.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Think\", \"from\": 4820, \"to\": 4847}, {\"ngram\": \"drives\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 4872}, {\"ngram\": \"holes\", \"from\": 4887, \"to\": 4892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 50 meters, he must make \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cprobably the most difficult decision\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d in that race.How am I going to stay in the middle of the lane?\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 5066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"50 meters\", \"from\": 4937, \"to\": 4946}, {\"ngram\": \"the most difficult decision\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 4973, \"to\": 5003}, {\"ngram\": \"that race\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5016}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 5043, \"to\": 5053}, {\"ngram\": \"the lane\", \"from\": 5057, \"to\": 5065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many coaches, he says, tell sprinters to lean in at the turn.\", \"from\": 5067, \"to\": 5128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many coaches\", \"from\": 5067, \"to\": 5079}, {\"ngram\": \"sprinters\", \"from\": 5095, \"to\": 5104}, {\"ngram\": \"the turn\", \"from\": 5119, \"to\": 5127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not accurate.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He wants to turn his hips, gradually, and the comparison he invokes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a car\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s headlights\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094makes his point easy to understand, even though he calls them \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009clight beams.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He holds both hands near his hips to demonstrate.\", \"from\": 5129, \"to\": 5381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his hips\", \"from\": 5175, \"to\": 5183}, {\"ngram\": \"the comparison\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5214}, {\"ngram\": \"his point\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5266}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009clight beams.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 5313, \"to\": 5331}, {\"ngram\": \"both hands\", \"from\": 5341, \"to\": 5351}, {\"ngram\": \"his hips\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lean and those light beams point right, toward the stands.\", \"from\": 5382, \"to\": 5440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those light beams\", \"from\": 5391, \"to\": 5408}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 5429, \"to\": 5439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gradually turn the hips and they point the same way as the body.\", \"from\": 5441, \"to\": 5505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hips\", \"from\": 5456, \"to\": 5464}, {\"ngram\": \"the same way\", \"from\": 5480, \"to\": 5492}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 75 meters, maybe 80, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s time to start putting power into the ground, as you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re coming out of this turn,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he says.\", \"from\": 5507, \"to\": 5634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"75 meters\", \"from\": 5510, \"to\": 5519}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 5541, \"to\": 5545}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 5563, \"to\": 5568}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 5574, \"to\": 5584}, {\"ngram\": \"you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 5589, \"to\": 5597}, {\"ngram\": \"this turn\", \"from\": 5612, \"to\": 5621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIf you let up, in this part of the turn, you will not get the effect of all the work you did back there.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Another check of lane positioning.\", \"from\": 5635, \"to\": 5781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this part\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5665}, {\"ngram\": \"the turn\", \"from\": 5669, \"to\": 5677}, {\"ngram\": \"the effect\", \"from\": 5696, \"to\": 5706}, {\"ngram\": \"all the work\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5722}, {\"ngram\": \"there.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Another check\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5759}, {\"ngram\": \"lane positioning\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 5779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, more power, more speed.\", \"from\": 5782, \"to\": 5811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Then, more power\", \"from\": 5782, \"to\": 5798}, {\"ngram\": \"more speed\", \"from\": 5800, \"to\": 5810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo we can continue to have that energy that we built up, flowing with us, going down the track.\", \"from\": 5812, \"to\": 5910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that energy\", \"from\": 5842, \"to\": 5853}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5885, \"to\": 5887}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 5900, \"to\": 5909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, this is where you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re going to feel the best momentum.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d As the turn gives way to the straightway, the final sprint toward the finish line, Lyles says many athletes \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009crelease\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d their body, meaning they start to relax.\", \"from\": 5911, \"to\": 6138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6059, \"end\": 6064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9986971900510467, \"rank\": 0.0013041508886494004, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 5930, \"to\": 5938}, {\"ngram\": \"the best momentum.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 5953, \"to\": 5974}, {\"ngram\": \"the turn\", \"from\": 5978, \"to\": 5986}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 5993, \"to\": 5996}, {\"ngram\": \"the straightway\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6015}, {\"ngram\": \"the final sprint\", \"from\": 6017, \"to\": 6033}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 6041, \"to\": 6056}, {\"ngram\": \"many athletes\", \"from\": 6069, \"to\": 6082}, {\"ngram\": \"their body\", \"from\": 6097, \"to\": 6107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This can push their momentum outside of their lane, or force them to \\u00e2\\u0