\", \"from\": 6541, \"to\": 6549}, {\"ngram\": \"na feel.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Interestingly\", \"from\": 6553, \"to\": 6578}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 6580, \"to\": 6585}, {\"ngram\": \"separate 100-meter aims\", \"from\": 6611, \"to\": 6634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 30 meters of the second 100, he says, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s time to commit\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094to body position, to knees hammering into the track, to keeping those shoulders forward.\", \"from\": 6637, \"to\": 6790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"30 meters\", \"from\": 6640, \"to\": 6649}, {\"ngram\": \"commit\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094to body position\", \"from\": 6693, \"to\": 6718}, {\"ngram\": \"knees\", \"from\": 6723, \"to\": 6728}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 6744, \"to\": 6753}, {\"ngram\": \"those shoulders\", \"from\": 6766, \"to\": 6781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If those go back, energy escapes upward, unnecessarily.\", \"from\": 6791, \"to\": 6846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 6809, \"to\": 6815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m gonna ask you: what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s your favorite cloud?\", \"from\": 6847, \"to\": 6900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 6847, \"to\": 6855}, {\"ngram\": \"your favorite cloud\", \"from\": 6880, \"to\": 6899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, if you tell me, you failed.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d At 180 meters, mental focus becomes paramount.\", \"from\": 6901, \"to\": 6984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"180 meters\", \"from\": 6940, \"to\": 6950}, {\"ngram\": \"mental focus\", \"from\": 6952, \"to\": 6964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sprinters must follow what their coaches taught them, as close as possible to their chosen ideal form.\", \"from\": 6985, \"to\": 7087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sprinters\", \"from\": 6985, \"to\": 6994}, {\"ngram\": \"their coac